1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
I was in a three-year friends-with-benefits 
relationship with a famous superhero actress.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
We met at an industry event through a mutual friend.
At first, I didn’t even realize who she was.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,000
She just had this wild, magnetic energy.

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:17,000
We kept bumping into each other —
parties, premieres, late-night texts.

5
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:22,000
It wasn’t just physical. We’d hang out,
watch movies, talk about life.

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:26,500
She said I was her calm in the chaos.

7
00:00:26,500 --> 00:00:32,000
When she got married, it ended quietly.
No drama. Just closure.

8
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:37,500
We still talk sometimes — no tension, no regrets.
Just a secret that never made the tabloids.

9
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:42,000
What would you confess?
